---
title: Mapo Tofu
tags: quick and easy, tofu
servings: 3
cook time: 10 minutes
ai_image: true
date added: 2026-03-21
---

Cut @tofu{1%block} into 1-inch cubes. Heat @House Foods Mapo Tofu Sauce{1%packet} in a #skillet{} over medium heat. Add the tofu cubes and gently stir to coat. Simmer for ~{5%minutes} until heated through. Serve over @steamed rice{}.
